        "text": " they render ‘record’ and ‘bear record,’ they render in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "John 8:17-18",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ‘witness’ and ‘bear witness.’ The latter rendering is to be preferred. The Pharisees attempt to cancel the effect of Christ’s impressive declaration by urging against Him a formal objection, the validity of which He had been heard to admit (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "John 5:31",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "): ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Thou bearest",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "witness",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "of Thyself; Thy",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "witness",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "is not true",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
